DebuggingPlugin - Class in de.lukaskoerfer.gradle.debugging
A Plugin that provides extended debugging functionality

Applying this plugin will do the following: Register ExtendedDebugConfiguration methods to add customized debug JVM options on each task that implements JavaForkOptions Register a container for debugging configurations.
